</quote>
<pc>”</pc>太祖又詔諭之<pc>，</pc>煜乃聽命<pc>。</pc>
</p>
</div>
<div>
<p>
<date when="963">
<date notBefore="960" notAfter="963">建隆</date>
<measure quantity="4" unit="years">
<num value="4">四</num>年</measure>
</date>
<pc>，</pc>遣使朝貢<pc>。</pc>是冬<pc>，</pc>又貢白金<num value="10000">萬</num>兩<pc>，</pc>乳香茶藥<num value="10000">萬</num>斤<pc>。</pc>煜複上言<pc>，</pc>請寢洪進恩命<pc>。</pc>太祖又以諭煜<pc>。</pc>
<date when="964">
